data.description:
Welcome to your new home at 719 N 13th St, Waco, Texas! This charming abode, built in 2020, offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and convenience. Boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, it's an ideal sanctuary for first-time homebuyers eager to embark on their homeownership journey.

Situated conveniently close to downtown Waco, you'll enjoy easy access to the city's vibrant heart while relishing the tranquility of your own space. The property features a good-sized lot, offering ample space for outdoor activities, entertaining guests, or creating a playground for kids and furry friends.

Discover a bright, airy interior thoughtfully designed to maximize space and functionality. The open layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings and everyday living.

With its prime location, contemporary amenities, and versatile outdoor space, 719 N 13th St presents an irresistible opportunity to call Waco home. Take your chance to make this gem yours and start creating unforgettable memories in your new abode!
